21635037@unknown@formal@none@1@S@Asset-backed securities "are an attractive investment compared to bank certificates of deposit or other corporate bonds," says Craig J. Goldberg, managing director and head of the asset-backed securities group at Merrill Lynch Capital Markets.@@@@1@34@@oe@2-2-2013
